name: Supay Bull
description:
/This is the Toro Supay, popular myth of Stgo del Estero.
Please make sure your greed doesn't lead you to him!/

The Supay Bull is one of the personifications of the Devil (Supay) in Santiago del Estero. 

The popular tale confers on him incredible powers, which allow him to protect and grant unbelievable wealth and prosperity to those who make a pact with him. However, when death comes for the beneficiary, the Supay Bull will not only take their soul, but will also destroy the estate they protected, leaving nothing but ruins and death in his wake.
